Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 全部做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟为了告白很努力做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 好想死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚 麦没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:31.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果那之后直到隔天的傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦就只给我发了一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好气啊 真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他告白成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:51.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,傻的吗 她肯定是在骗你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:58.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都是想要被玩弄感情的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:05.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 真的好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,轻井泽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,失恋旅行？伤心旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是两人份的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:05.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 有一个人根本就没有开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是避暑胜地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,风吹得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是多亏了这一带的雾和地形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:19.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不知道我们俩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在只有我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候就会变得很强势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的表情 好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:45.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 干点别的事能更好分散注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我失恋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 小绘你家真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在轻井泽还有别墅什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 不是我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是亲戚家的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有点旧呢 不要抱太大期望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:13.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:18.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不在 今天起就是我们两人独处了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃 味道很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗也觉得好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当然好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是笃也做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘的表弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,侧脸看起来好像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 你先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 洗碗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 你很累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有点害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,景色倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:42.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 这里的厨房意外的窄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:45.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有多生气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:48.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗就算生气也超美的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧洗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没带换洗的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我管你 不想的话就离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 搞得湿哒哒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么外面感觉挺热闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:18.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来你为什么会知道旅行的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你家打了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难得能跟花火两人独处的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火失恋了 跟那家伙也分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想在这次旅行攻略她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但都因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:47.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你心知肚明 她是不可能喜欢上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在最后想要一个回忆罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗你的声音比较大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要美满彻底地结束这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不可以这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想让你美满彻底地结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:10.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得你并没有坚强到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天绝对不准进房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说你的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 到底哪里不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别人又了解我的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,身体好热呢 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚洗完澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的我 一直不曾给别人看过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也没想过让别人了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是并不是只有我们两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他就在隔壁房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要抑制住声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:07.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使触碰过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:08.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是选择了孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹让我自己来决定结局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:40.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:46.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去往轻井泽的新干线车票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还在发抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 虽然我只有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:10.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,内心已经脆弱到 被谁触碰就仿佛要崩塌一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,心也一直在呼吸着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:31.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,起的真早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我平常都不怎么去看湖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你回答我就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我应该问得再简单点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先想清楚你对早苗的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以当成别人的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请你在旅行结束前想好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:54.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好棒 情绪高涨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘很喜欢衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,买了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超级满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连暑假打短工的钱都用掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经好久都没见到小绘这么开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,树荫下就是令人平静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别乱扔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗她 不可以当成别人的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事 我明明就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在起了独占欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:50.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:52.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和一开始并没有两样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:55.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感情只是暂时的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:56.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这份感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:03.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:09.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不要给这份感情冠上任何名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这会是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:24.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要在关键的时候大声喊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在玩这么老的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有老游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:40.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,免得传染给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请你在旅行结束前想好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:55.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又死了 真是讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,第几次了都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘好弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火意外的擅长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候经常在哥哥家玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:11.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:19.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火一直喜欢的是钟井老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被彻底拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说我现在痛快多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是哭的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火很努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,勇敢地去面对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我无论做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法影响你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘 有件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这次该轮到我得出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你陪我到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:13:59.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为花火很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止一直利用这点很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:13.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你纵容我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:16.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很享受 也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:24.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用你的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,任性的人也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无所谓了 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我已经放弃你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行之前我就决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果花火失恋后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:42.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以那种眼光看待我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就离开火花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:55.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就分开睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上我们各回各的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:04.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:07.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实一点也不温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:14.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 我也有想要告诉你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:22.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,继续和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你说的话有多残酷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还说做朋友什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多么喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:53.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 我的软弱 我的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让你如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这次 我绝对不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:05.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的感情不需要任何人了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做就等于孤独啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是继续现在的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是在这里结束关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘的心门就这么一直关闭着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过 孤独没什么不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再闯入我的内心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我想了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:33.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想继续了解你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要你告诉我 无论什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我会等到你习惯为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的我一定不是什么好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我该怎么振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一个人就无法活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我终于注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:09.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼神也和我一样 充满着胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:12.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道什么时候能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是非常喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会努力…忘了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不得不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却有着不想忘记的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 已经回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 赶的首班车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 完全没说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行啦 病人就老实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,病人就快点退烧赶紧滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗你不是还有我在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:14.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也稍微信任你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:23.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在谁都无法预测未来会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我相信未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种信念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像护身符一样 虽然微小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却能点亮心房 让人倍感温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:43.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,时隔多日的学校 教室 谈话声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,令人感到不自在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感到不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可又有什么办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使依然感到心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛到刻骨铭心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸥端同学在狂啃面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这画面真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是太饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 一脸阴沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 一个人回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成你也被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫「也」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你从头到尾都是被甩的命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？你这人真是令人生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁气人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么 你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我对麦的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比你更长久 更直接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:53.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我现在痛快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:02.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去小卖部买的酥饼才更好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:05.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也试着自己迈出脚步就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然意识到 在这世界上 我变得孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是呆呆地站在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:20.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么都没想过 一个人向前迈出脚步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是家访吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前就一直想试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和家长寒暄 然后帮我泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:39.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别装老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会停的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:46.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:50.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:58.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「老师」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:20:59.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:03.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的只是做一下家访而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 家长不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学生又是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:15.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:17.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如同你我的影子般延伸着 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}将胆小怯懦归咎于时代的错也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无处可归的我 找寻着愿望的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只愿成为你唇边溢出的只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}带上无法实现的希冀 以及毫无底气的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}倘若感情全部流失殆尽 便由我开始描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如今向你我的影子伸出手 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影のように伸びている　あぁ平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}勇気がないのは時代のせいにしてしまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何処にも行けない　願いの居場所を探してた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君の唇から　こぼれだす　言葉になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そんな叶わない望みも　不甲斐ない声も引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}感情全部流しきったら　描き始めてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影に今手を伸ばす　あぁ平行線
